Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.85,0:01:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,〔如此温柔的赤井美月〕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.02,0:01:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（创纪录的大热门名作肉感漫画真人版！)-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.10,0:01:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次因为事故无法取材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.68,0:01:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子不行…那是情报社的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.89,0:01:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在公司工作是看结果的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.86,0:01:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说也没法去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.00,0:01:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.57,0:01:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.50,0:01:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们二人到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.77,0:02:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子会开不完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.05,0:02:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,课长这么说的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也没意见吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.60,0:02:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤井美月进公司1年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.08,0:02:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常像刚才那样和同事吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.92,0:02:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很冷淡，和同事不好相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.53,0:03:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是有了传闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.07,0:03:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以得多注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.85,0:03:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,课长，今天怎么办？\N难得这时候，但实在不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.49,0:03:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去接女儿了吗去？\N没关系，他在老婆娘家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.60,0:03:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.77,0:03:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走吧…也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.97,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在吗？…  回来了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.78,0:04:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也才刚买回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.45,0:04:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好…麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.82,0:04:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎么的，就走到这样一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.67,0:04:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她刚来公司司几个月时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.41,0:04:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为发生了一个不可容忍的失误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.45,0:05:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来她和我一起解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.40,0:05:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是部下的问题，但责任在我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.71,0:05:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果当然是极差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.85,0:05:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤井，辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.90,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就这么哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.54,0:06:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就这么不自禁地摸了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.09,0:06:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直以为可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.44,0:06:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人受不住女人的泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.78,0:06:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能这么听着她哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.66,0:06:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等回过神来，已经和她上床了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.67,0:06:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么有了关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.22,0:07:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我像你这年纪的时侯，也会和人争吵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.16,0:07:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有到我现在这年纪才能体会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.67,0:07:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是年轻时的争一囗气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.98,0:07:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，这是．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.02,0:07:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，这是．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，这是... ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.22,0:07:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想说很可爱就买了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.50,0:07:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.61,0:08:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越久就越是说不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.80,0:11:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用着好湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.77,0:13:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱，一直有反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.58,0:13:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是女儿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.53,0:14:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…爸，你听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.95,0:14:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸，你在做什么？？ …没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.48,0:14:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成有人？…没有的事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.76,0:14:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.25,0:15:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是女人吗？原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.69,0:15:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打扰了吧…才没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.76,0:15:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很行嘛~ 才不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.56,0:15:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会对妈保密的…想什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.51,0:15:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了，妈也对爸没什么了--
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.71,0:15:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.78,0:15:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.85,0:15:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人的直觉真准，可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.37,0:15:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很不错，下次再和你说…嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.14,0:15:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要期待啊…知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.88,0:16:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安…和大家问好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.46,0:16:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想要就自己来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.59,0:16:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.43,0:16:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴里面都是会让人震惊的灼热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.04,0:17:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那热气和汗，真让人受不了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.20,0:17:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好深好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.16,0:18:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那身体一直吸夹着老二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.28,0:18:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任谁都会忘情在这身体上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.90,0:19:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.28,0:20:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人有种回到年轻的感觉-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.55,0:20:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.79,0:21:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.88,0:22:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.22,0:22:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.30,0:23:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.77,0:24:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.32,0:25:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.34,0:25:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.52,0:26:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.37,0:26:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:00.77,0:27:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:35.21,0:27:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次可以吗\N随你用吧…还这么想要啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.07,0:28:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.37,0:28:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:36.27,0:28:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.74,0:28:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢吗？…好喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:13.87,0:29:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:27.92,0:29:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:35.96,0:29:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:08.26,0:30:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.40,0:30:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.58,0:31:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.75,0:32:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也许和他爸一样大了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.73,0:32:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以其实面对的就像女儿一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:40.31,0:32:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这却是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:54.36,0:32:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得这其实很可爱冯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.27,0:33:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那去找啊…不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.64,0:33:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能看能不能慢慢忘却
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.79,0:33:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:24.32,0:33:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:38.00,0:33:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木，你念一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:40.61,0:33:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木，你念一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:49.38,0:33:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊？... 看你何时回都行呐，念一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:52.09,0:33:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊？... 看你何时回都行呐，念一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:58.63,0:34:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情书吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:03.10,0:34:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一看就知道了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:10.80,0:34:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次，怎么办好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:16.41,0:34:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人向你告白没交往过？假的吧？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:24.88,0:34:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没说谎.--看来是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:34.26,0:34:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:38.73,0:34:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那和我交往吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:44.87,0:34:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（3小时后）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:52.31,0:34:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次如何？．．脑子一片空白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:59.62,0:35:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:06.16,0:35:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好吗？．．不知道怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:17.27,0:35:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃第一次好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:24.61,0:35:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:27.85,0:35:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看，好多啊，好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:35.12,0:35:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真浪费，我吃了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:56.94,0:35:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么好吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:11.12,0:36:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.50,0:36:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又硬了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.83,0:36:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又硬了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.87,0:36:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又硬了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.90,0:36:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又硬了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:25.34,0:36:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我住这里，搞到天亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:31.71,0:36:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家人怎么办？．．没问颗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.58,0:36:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就么决定吧．太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:43.22,0:36:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里要不行了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:14.52,0:37:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好激烈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:38.11,0:37:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:44.72,0:37:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很容易去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:49.66,0:37:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽会很可怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:00.80,0:38:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会害羞…抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:07.54,0:38:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:14.01,0:38:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:17.28,0:38:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.36,0:38:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求好多啊…都这样的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.27,0:38:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:38.87,0:38:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:43.51,0:38:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:56.82,0:39:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快要受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:03.80,0:39:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为爱上我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:58.45,0:39:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:12.99,0:41:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:31.22,0:45:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:18.86,0:47:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶爽吗？…好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:54.96,0:47:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想插入呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:00.80,0:48:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？… 好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:57.88,0:50:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶得好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:09.79,0:51:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
